data.description: Welcome to a home designed for everyday living. This residence is situated on nearly 3/4 acres. As you enter, you're greeted by a living area with vaulted ceilings that seamlessly blend with the kitchen & dining spaces. The kitchen is well-equipped, featuring an island that provides ample counter space. The expansive primary bedroom, complete with a comfortable sitting area. Its adjoining five-piece bathroom is designed for ultimate relaxation. 3 additional bedrooms ensure space for everyone. Outdoors, there's a vast covered patio & a massive, fully-fenced backyard. The property also offers a 2-car garage & dedicated RV parking. Enhancing the home's versatility is a DADU, perfect for guests or potential rental opportunities.
